                    <div class='commenttext'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span style="font-size: 120%;">#29 hippykidz</span></strong> @ 10:24 am August 19th, 2008</span><br />
<p>I get a minimum of four dinners from a whole bird. Using a variety of the same techniques above. If the bird is large enough the meals will yeild at least one lunch portion of left overs. I have a background in food service and sometimes forget that this stuff is not just something everyone does. You know &#8220;todays special is tommorrows soup&#8221; and all.</p>
