<p>BTW:  Even with the frozen chicken breasts, if you thaw and then cook them with a little EVOO, you can get a good bit of concentrated broth.  Pour them into ice cube trays, and all you need to do when you want some broth is add one to your slow cooker, or in a pot of stew, etc.  Nice and convenient.</p>
